Downloads|⇒ tree apache-tomcat-8.0.35/webapps/ROOT/WEB-INF
apache-tomcat-8.0.35/webapps/ROOT/WEB-INF
├── classes
│   └── com
│       └── afterqcd
│           └── study
│               └── servlet
│                   └── clz
│                       └── HelloServlet.class  # 由HelloServlet编译得到
└── web.xml # 即为web.xml.bak

运行流程:
* 编译: mvn clean install
* 拷贝classes: mv target/classes $TOMCAT_HOME/webapps/ROOT/WEB-INF/
* 拷贝web.xml: mv src/main/java/com/afterqcd/study/servlet/clz/web.xml.bak $TOMCAT_HOME/webapps/ROOT/WEB-INF/web.xml